thankyou_planting: Thank you for planting {{count}} trees with us! We've sent an email confirmation to you. If your donation was to a tax deductible project, you will receive an email with a donation receipt in time.
donate_trees_description: Plant trees for the future of the children! Explore planting projects around the world and help plant more trees with just a few clicks. Together we are on our way to a trillion trees.
